@startuml
title UC001 - Control Flow Diagram (User Account Creation)
start

:1. User enters username, email, password, retype password;
:2. Submit form;

if (3. Is username/email valid?) then (yes)
  if (4. Do passwords match?) then (yes)
    if (5. Is username/email duplicate?) then (no)
      :6. Create new user account;
      :7. Redirect to login;
      stop
    else (yes)
      --> [Retry]
    endif
  else (no)
    --> [Retry]
  endif
else (no)
  --> [Retry]
endif

:8. [Retry] Display error and allow user to retry;
stop
@enduml
